{"type":"message","id":"cf30d5a1","parentId":"b63c6397","timestamp":"2026-03-24T04:12:56.758Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_pqgd5plxrc9r_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 5538\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=3790\n[file inferred from ACTION] temporal_invariance_classifier.py\n[mutation proposed] temporal_invariance_classifier.py\n[master a6da271] pulse: 2026-03-24 001230\n 6 files changed, 427 insertions(+), 40 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 001230.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 001230.mutation\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 001230 - The TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next critical step to validate the COMPRESSION-CAUSAL DUALITY hypothesis. I need to implement a classifier that identifies invariants across pulse logs and tests prediction accuracy.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"quick-dune","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 5538\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=3790\n[file inferred from ACTION] temporal_invariance_classifier.py\n[mutation proposed] temporal_invariance_classifier.py\n[master a6da271] pulse: 2026-03-24 001230\n 6 files changed, 427 insertions(+), 40 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 001230.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 001230.mutation\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 001230 - The TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next critical step to validate the COMPRESSION-CAUSAL DUALITY hypothesis. I need to implement a classifier that identifies invariants across pulse logs and tests prediction accuracy.\n","name":"powershell Bypass"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774325576755}}
